<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/25425079">父母给 4 到 5 岁的男孩讲述空气动力学，是否合适？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2352662" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">吃饭时，邻座父亲给大概四、五岁的小男孩讲解空气动力学。</div>


</div>
